    Callback interface invoked for promises that are either fulfilled or rejected.

    Callback interface for rejected promises.
    Promise.OnTapCallback<V>
    Callback interface used for Promise.tap(OnTapCallback) used to observe fulfilled promises without modifying the next promise.
